## Cohesion Check Complete: Hailee-Steinfeld.md

**Before score: 8/10**
**After score: 9/10**

### Central Thesis
Hailee Steinfeld is an Enneagram Type 3 who converts every achievement into debt, because the applause always landed on her output and never the self underneath, so she can't read evidence she's arrived as proof she has.

### Changes Made (2 total)

**Transition Fixes (2):**
- **"Why the Oscar Didn't Count" → "How She Keeps Vanishing"**: Added a forward bridge at the end of the prep section ("All of that is control over how the work looks. What she does with the work itself, when she keeps a lane and when she walks away from it, runs on the same need."). Carries the *control* keyword into the vanishing section and reframes "leaving" as control before the reader hits the cold open, without spoiling the section's own paragraph-4 reveal.
- **"How She Keeps Vanishing" → "What She Sounds Like When She's Lost"**: Added a two-sentence bridge connecting the newsletter (built during the 2023 strike) to the shutdown that same strike caused ("She built that newsletter during the strike. What it does not show is the state she built it out of."). Turns the shared strike from an apparent repeat into clear cause-and-effect.

