None structural. The one thing a reader *might* notice is the diagnosis → skirt and skirt → Oscar boundaries lean on implicit "wound/pattern" links rather than explicit bridges, but both are adequate and the skirt is pre-seeded in the intro, so I left them. Your call if you want those tightened too, but I'd leave them; over-bridging would flatten the punchy section openers that are working.
